data.description: Great ranch style home close to downtown Lapeer with 122 ft of frontage between 2 lots!  Three bedrooms and two full baths, hardwood floors throughout and a finished basement with a great family area and two extra rooms with closets and an egress window!  Open concept living area and kitchen with eat at bar and tons of counter space.  The roof was replaced in 2022.    Sale includes the property adjacent to the home currently fenced in: L20-24-102-040-00 CITY OF LAPEER ORIGINAL PLAT NE 1/4 BLK 6 SE'LY 1/2 OF LOTS 7 & 8, ALSO NW'LY 3 FT OF VAC BIDDLE ST ADJ THERETO (L=1 P=73 SEC 5, T7N-R10E)  Seller holds a current real estate license with the State of Michigan.
